Privacy Policy
Details on how we handle your privacy
AuroraReach and the operating company HuskyCodes Oy takes your privacy seriously. To better protect your privacy we provide this privacy policy notice explaining the way your personal information is collected and used.
Collection of Routine Information
This service tracks basic information about their users. This information includes, but is not limited to, IP addresses, browser/app details, timestamps and referring pages. None of this information can personally identify specific user to this service. The information is tracked for routine administration, insights and maintenance purposes.
Privacy Rights
In accordance with GDPR, we offer various tools and services to comply with following data rights:
You have the option to easily download your data from My Account page. It will be in common format such as txt and csv making it easy to infer.
You can delete your account and data at any time with immediate effect fom My Account page.
You have the option to update/correct your profile information at any time.
You have the ability to opt-in or opt-out of direct marketing.
Data Collected and Processed
This service requires certain personal data to provide the service, which will be collected only when required and when user specifically agrees.
Your email is required to create an unique account and allow transactional email such as password resets. Users have the ability to opt-in or opt-out of email marketing.
Device information is collected when you subscribe for push notifications. Also it makes it easier for user to subscribe to other cities without haing to add device each time.
Phonenumbers are only collected when partners give them, we do not save data such as phonenumbers for users.
Subscription start and end dates are recorded for gaining insights into service popularity.
How and when users interact with cities and/or partners are recorded for for gaining insights. This includes anonymized details such as platform, localized region of access and what service/locations you interested with. This information is anonymized and shown to partipating partners for only their specific created resources.
This personal data is deleted and anonymized via online delete my account functionality. We will follow legal requirements as to keeping track of billing details for a given time after accounts have been deleted.
Opting out of Tracking
Our applications and website has been designed to allow you to configure via consent forms for opting out of ads and where no dialog is present we use configured browser settings when available and given.
