Interest-based Advertising:
Our platform acknowledges and discloses Google's use of device IDs and demographic information for interest-based advertising. This section of our Privacy Policy clarifies how targeted advertising is facilitated through the collection and analysis of user data, ensuring users are aware of personalized ad experiences based on their interests and online activities.
Our application utilizes Interest-Based Advertising (IBA) services provided by Google, which helps in delivering ads that are more relevant to your interests. This is achieved by collecting information about your online activities, such as the apps you use, the websites you visit, and the searches you make. Google uses this information to infer your interests, demographics (such as age and gender), and other data to provide targeted advertisements that are more likely to be of interest to you. We want to inform you that for the purpose of providing interest-based ads, Google may use device IDs, cookies, and other identifiers, along with your demographic information. We are committed to providing transparency and control over the use of your data in interest-based advertising, and we encourage you to review your ad settings and privacy options available within Google's services to customize your ad experience.
COPPA
In adherence to the Children's Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA), our platform has incorporated stringent guidelines for apps and sites directed towards children under 13. This includes a rigorous verification process to ensure compliance with COPPA, highlighting our commitment to safeguarding children's privacy and requiring explicit parental consent for data collection where applicable.
Cookies
Where necessary, this service uses cookies to store information about a visitorâ€™s preferences and history in order to better serve the visitor and/or present the visitor with customized content.
Google Admob and related technologies might make use of cookies to better deliver personalized ads when configured. These technologies are employed by Google AdMob and other advertising services on our platform to collect data for optimizing ad delivery. It is essential for users to understand that these cookies and web beacons help in tailoring advertisements to their preferences and analyzing ad performance.
Links to Third Party Websites
we have included links on this service for your use and reference. we are not responsible for the privacy policies on these websites. You should be aware that the privacy policies of these websites may differ from our own.
Security
The security of your personal information is important to us, but remember that no method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage, is 100% secure. While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your personal information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.
In the event of any data breach, you will be informed of any such events with actions on how to protect yourself.
Changes To This Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy is effective as of 25 March 2021 (the original published date) and will remain in effect except with respect to any changes in its provisions in the future, which will be in effect immediately after being posted on this page.
we reserve the right to update or change our Privacy Policy at any time and you should check this Privacy Policy periodically.
